  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508570/extras/0639ce057d0569464b8cc5c70abf00e1.avif?t=1733273349\" width=616 height=347 /></span><br>It's your summer break right in the middle of summer heat.<br>You are alone in your apartment, bored with too much time in your hand.<br>Then, you received a phone call.<br>「We'll be going for a trip. Can you come over and look after Hazuki during the summer?」<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508570/extras/1875eadb5603cbd27a99e2fd5a95c8ec.avif?t=1733273349\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br>Your childhood friend Hazuki lives in a relaxing countryside surrounded by nature.<br>It's probably healthier for you to stay here rather than your apartment in the hot and humid city.<br>You hurry to prepare yourself for a trip to the countryside.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508570/extras/100e393104a023434c023e7af77a6844.avif?t=1733273349\" width=616 height=346 /></span><br><br><br><br><strong>～Communicate With Your Childhood Friend～</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508570/extras/8053e5738feaf14a784accdeb7d0b2b0.avif?t=1733273349\" width=210 height=350 /></span><br><strong>Hazuki</strong><br>A quiet girl who is rather mature for her age.<br><br><br><br>She's also carefreely relaxing at home during her summer break.<br>Interact with her and build your friendship.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508570/extras/e22a56f8e1179a3340dbfdf21ddc5681.avif?t=1733273349\" width=616 height=343 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508570/extras/f9e668f96117f46af672aeaf941ed812.avif?t=1733273349\" width=616 height=341 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508570/extras/fdbd6caf1dfbee94b81aa43a03751e4a.avif?t=1733273349\" width=616 height=345 /></span><br><br><br><br><strong>～Your childhood friend is becoming an adult～</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1508570/extras/e260b227f02b0326fe1013d404f81c7c.avif?t=1733273349\" width=285 height=525 /></span>",
